{
  "stem": "942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I found out since then that over 200,000 Jewish people were killed on these death marches from all the other camps, and including Auschwitz-- you know, that we were being marched west, you know.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So here we are that night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember the artillery-- the Red Army was just miles away, and the artillery barrage, you know, and flashes of light, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember these [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Stalin ?] candles, they were dropping from planes, you know, that lit up the sky, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was really eerie.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were marching, you know, out in this forest and fields, you know, for about six days, day and night, nonstop.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably about 10,000 people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The column, you couldn't see the end or the beginning of it, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I know that I was trying to get to the front of the column, you know, because if you got straggled, you know, then you were in bad shape.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They would--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if you were in the front of the column, you, sort of, didn't have to walk as fast as if you were in the back, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Something, I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to go to the front of the column.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were walking five abreast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to hook our arms together, and whoever-- we slept, and we walked like zombies, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like, you know, you walked like a machine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't give us any food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know I had a piece of bread when I left Auschwitz, and that was gone soon.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, it was cold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- we ate snow, and I know, now, that that wasn't such a good idea.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
